snippet.title: Newer SUMMER SUN Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready for some fun in the sun? The Newer Team is proud to present the Newer Summer Sun special! So put on your sun hats and rub in the sunscreen, cause here we go!


Newer Summer Sun includes:

-23 full levels spanning five partial worlds
-Dozens of custom and retextured sprites scattered across the land
-All new arrangements of classic Mario tunes, composed in-house
-Brand new lighting effects and colours to dazzle the eyes
-Hundreds of other tweaks and fixes

Download: www.newerteam.com
